item.title: CVE-2016-10395|2024-08-06T03:21:51.436Z -- flexera%20software%20llc -- flexnet%20publisher
item.description: In FlexNet Publisher versions before Luton SP1 (11.14.1.1) running FlexNet Publisher Licensing Service on Windows platform, a boundary error related to a named pipe within the FlexNet Publisher Licensing Service can be exploited to cause an out-of-bounds memory read access and subsequently execute arbitrary code with SYSTEM privileges.
